istics, robust to defective and noisy information,\nand a very simple implementation which could be utilized as an alternative to\neither more expensive speaker-adaptation systems or of numerous manual\ncorrection sessions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Mar 2020 12:42:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Apr 2020 15:52:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-01"}
